Package: zoeken
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: __ARCH__
Maintainer: Greenstorm <sdussinger1007@gmail.com>
Depends: ca-certificates, adduser
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Greenstorm5417/zoeken
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/Greenstorm5417/zoeken.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/Greenstorm5417/zoeken
Description: SearXNG-compatible metasearch engine
 Zoeken is a metasearch engine with a Rust backend and React SPA,
 developed by Greenstorm.
 .
 This package installs the server binary, frontend assets, a systemd
 unit, configuration under /etc/zoeken, and the AGPL-3.0-or-later
 license texts under /usr/share/doc/zoeken.
